author: Fiona Blackwood
title: Hundreds of Airbnbs flood rental market amid COVID-19, relieving rental crunch
description: Tasmania has struggled with a housing crisis for more than a year, partly driven by a surge in short-stay accommodation. But as coronavirus puts a halt on travel, hundreds of properties have been added to the tight rental market.
